                <offset>0</offset>
                <text>﻿Case 4 is a male in his 20s born to Swiss unrelated parents.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>62</offset>
                <text>The patient was born after 38 weeks of gestation with a weight of 3110 g, a length of 51 cm, and 36 cm HC.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>169</offset>
