                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1115</offset>
                <text>At that time, weight was 55 kg (3–10th centile), length was 160 cm (−2.3 SD; 3rd centile), and HC was 59 cm (75–90th centile).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1242</offset>
                <text>He showed significant facial dysmorphism (figure 1D,E) with high broad forehead, long narrow face, short neck, laterally highly arched eyebrows, bilateral epicanthus, telecanthus with inner canthal distance of 4.5 cm (+4.3 SDS) and outer canthal distance of 9 cm (25–50th centile), broad flat nose, short philtrum, asymmetric ears with a right ear length of 7 cm (97th centile) and left ear length of 6 cm (25–50th centile), and retrognathia with a large chin.</text>
