            <sentence>
                <offset>1783</offset>
                <text>Metabolic testing, microscopic karyotyping and high resolution molecular karyotyping using an Affymetrix Cytogenetics 2.7 array showed normal results.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1934</offset>
                <text>Direct sequencing of KIF7 revealed the same mutations found in case 3 but with different parental origin: the intron 12 acceptor splice mutation c.2593-3C&gt;G is inherited from his mother while the exon 15 nonsense mutation c.3001C&gt;T, p.Gln1001X is inherited from his father.</text>
